messages.message:
*Search Feedback*
Search showed some strong opinions on the answer to my general question about our wellness stipend, even when I prompted it in different ways and made it reference different documents.

This is a tough problem to solve and shows that internal company text, even if misleading, can dictate the answer pretty strongly. Our various internal documents do mention Wellhub and use this language of "needing to download the Wellness Hub App" to use the $500 wellness credit for a tiered gym pass. In actuality, I wanted to know about the stipend and reimbursement process more generally.
